casebody.data:
Daly v. Georgia Power Company et al. No. 11835. November 27, 1937. Garl F. Hutcheson and G. E. Moore, for plaintiff. Colquitt, MacDougald, Troutman & Arkwright, Louis A. Burton, and Dudley Cook, for defendant.

Rehearing denied December, 15, 1937.

Bussell, C. J., Atkinson, P. J., and Hutcheson, J., being disqualified, Judges Gardner, Hardeman, and Smith were designated for this case.
